Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.62,0:01:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.70,0:01:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是汉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Hans
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎观赏可鱼童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And welcome to Fishy Fairy Tales
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪来着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where were we?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.29,0:01:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为大家献上经典童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Und now for a classic fairy tale
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.55,0:01:18.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名叫  黄雪王子与七只小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:18.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,called "Snow Yellow und the Seven Jellies"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(586,624)}黄雪王子\N与七只小水母
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.89,0:01:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前  有一个快乐的小王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Once upon a time, there was a happy little prince
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,名叫黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his name was Snow Yellow"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎哟喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie-daisy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我回去  疯疯小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:31.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back in there, you cuckoo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子住在一座城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Prince Snow Yellow lived in a castle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1394,920)}母
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,共住的是凯伦皇后  他的邪恶继主板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with Queen Karen, his evil Step-Motherboard"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是故事的反派
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the villain in this story
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幽默不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't that a hoot?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事始于一个美好的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our story begins on a beautiful day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与其他日子一般无二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like any other
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  我忠心的臣民们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, my loyal subjects
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you all
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.72,0:02:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你一点无价皇家珠宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here are some priceless royal jewels for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送给你  还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you and you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hellooo, Wishing Well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hellooo, Wishing Well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好一大早一起二重唱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for our morning duet?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I-I-I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对井许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a well-wisher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对井许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a well-wisher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许愿你平安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishing you well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许愿井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishing Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
