Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我许愿你平安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish you well
