Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我许愿你平安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish you well
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,许下心愿  祝福你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishes of wishing you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝福你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wishing you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早上没更新完就不准唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No singing until I've had my morning update
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  继母皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Queen Stepmommy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她哪弄来这么多水晶鞋的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is she getting all of these glass shoes?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Prince
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去洗皇家厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start scrubbing those royal commodes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然今天不准吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you don't eat today
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toilet duty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.32,0:03:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说你怎么突然样子变得这么方正了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, why do you look so square all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我长大了  就长出了棱角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My big boy edges just grew in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for noticing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  亲爱的继母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Queen Stepmommy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔镜魔镜挂墙上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic mirror on my wall
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个世上谁最方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's the squarest of them all?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后大人  你很方正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, my Queen, are square
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准确无误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'tis true
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但黄雪王子才是最方正的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Snow Yellow is the squarest
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啵啵哔嘟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boop-boop-bee-doo
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你本来就不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了你才知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't know anything until I told--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要想保住世上最方正的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I wanna stay the squarest in the land
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要让黄雪王子没资格再方正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need to de-squarify Prince Snow Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉挺有用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That works for me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huntsman?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huntsman?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后大人呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My Queen doth summon me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您呼唤我前来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You called for my personage--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my most--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至高无上方正殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,perfectly square Royal Highness?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去把王子带进森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are to take the Prince into the forest
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他的尖角剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and snip off his square corners
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是皇后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, my Queen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事我可不能做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could never do something like that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.93,0:05:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我打猎只找松露  不会剪海绵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a truffle hunter, not a sponge slicer
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay then
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就把你圆角切了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll cut off your corners
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个海绵尖角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you like those sponge corners
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要厚剪还是精剪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thick cut or deli sliced?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gooooo
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  皇后大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, my Queen
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然任务很讨厌  让他屁股有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even though the task was a pain in the rump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.26,0:06:08.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猎人还是低声下气去抓黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Huntsman pursued Snow Yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a cowardly chump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢点儿跑  王子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Moderate thy haste, my Prince
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你飞奔得也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're frolicking too fast
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot keep up
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有谁没吃第二顿早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone skipped their second breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先找下包包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me look in my satchel here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放在金托盘上的蟹皇堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A royal Krabby Patty on a golden platter
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's all for you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真好心  我不好意思把你搞残
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're too kind to mutilate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加奶酪行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about with cheese?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后要我剪掉你的尖角
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Queen wants me to cut off your corners
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.73,0:07:10.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样她才能成为世上最方正的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:10.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so she can be the squarest in the land
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑吧  我亲爱的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run, my sweet Prince
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲进树林里  永远别回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hide in the woods and never come back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你蟹皇堡就不用带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave thy Krabby Patty, though
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想变圆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna be round
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想一直方正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to stay square
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.12,0:07:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是暗黑深林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deep dark woods
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没那么可怕嘛  只要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're not that scary as long as you--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  好可爱的小巢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My, what a cute little hive
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以巢进躲里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can hive in the hide
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是躲进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or hide in the--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巢进
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hive in the--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hide for a while
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有人在家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is anybody home?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得看一眼里面  确保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some eyes on the inside to make sure it's safe
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸我得再找个地方住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Papa needs a new place to live
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像有小小的人住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like tiny people live here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.02,0:09:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可爱了  但是乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so cute but such a mess
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mon cherie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还得用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need these
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七张小椅子  上面都刻了名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seven little chairs, each with a name
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但这里也太脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this place is a dump
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really a shame
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来这里正适合当我藏身处的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It would make a perfect hideaway
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许要是我打扫干净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, maybe if I clean it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巢主就会同意我住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they'll let me stay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toilet duty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这么一件事  绝对充满刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now there's just one thing, with a ring-a-ding-ding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想快乐干活  那就得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get in the swing while you work, you--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用颤音高唱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,warble
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, well
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果陷入困境  全身无力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If it gets tough and your energy is sapped
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.00,0:10:15.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候打个盹最好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:15.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sometimes it's best to take a nap
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王子浅浅打了个盹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"While the Prince took a quick nappy-poo,
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此时住在巢里的七只小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"the seven jellies who live in the hive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正快乐地劳作着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,were happily at work"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开采海底小花花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We mine flowers of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酿出香甜水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we can make sweet jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还可以赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I can make me money
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这花粉味道真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This pollen sure smells funny
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别劳作了  你们这群白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop working, ya morons
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经五点了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's 5:00
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中咧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bingo
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七只小水母接着回到家中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"When the seven jellies got home"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没料到会发现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"They did not expect to find
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房进了一只打呼的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a snoring monster in their kitchen"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.02,0:11:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们一定就是这座可爱小巢的巢主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be the owners of this lovely little hive
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必多说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在可爱小椅子上看到了你们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw your names on your adorable little chairs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:08.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me guess
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是果果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must be Nutty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正中红心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hit the bull's-eye there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是蟹蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're Krusty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jackpot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芙芙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Puffy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is correct
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呆呆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:25.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老老
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cooty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're darn tootin'
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有蜗蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请问你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The question is, who are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来我们家干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what are you doing in our house?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you must be
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drippy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice to
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.24,0:12:47.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:47.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Meet ya
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Snow Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow Yellow?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个王子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Prince?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  而且我有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I'm in a dangerous pickle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:56.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1160,920)}腌椰菜
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一切都始于
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all started when--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pickle?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一切都始于
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all started when
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔镜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mirror
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.55,0:13:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王子向小水母们叙述着他的悲惨故事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"While the Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tells his harrowing story to the jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而猎人则在欺骗皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"the Huntsman was feeding lies to the Queen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说自己剪掉了王子的尖角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"about cutting off the Prince's corners
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后相信了  心满又意足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And she ate it up with great relish"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔镜魔镜挂墙上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic mirror on the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这个世上谁最
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now who's the squarest one of--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别浪费口水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Save your breath
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,王子一样还是方的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Prince is still square
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:30.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,提醒你一下  猎人是在骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Huntsman is lying, if you weren't aware
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lying?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从未受过如此奇耻大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have never been so offended in my--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要相信谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you gonna believe
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,信我  还是信那怪镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me or some loopy looking glass?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然相信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe you, of course
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我相信你可以当鳄鱼饵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe you're alligator bait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:13:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果想要剪了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want someone cut right
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须亲手去剪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to cut 'em yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.62,0:14:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿这身奇装异服  王子绝对认不出我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Prince will never recognize me in this wacky getup
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把这球有毒海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll dip this ball of poison chum
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裹进糖衣里  让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a candy coating that no one can resist
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是凯伦皇后悄悄前去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"So Queen Karen snuck away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七只小水母的巢  接着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:43.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the seven jellies' hive and"--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以自己翻页  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can turn my own pages, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢你们让我在这过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for letting me crash here a while
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我晚上会做水母堡当晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll grill jelly patties for dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也会想你的  蜗蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll miss you too, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躲猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peekaboo
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  方正到不行的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, my sickeningly square friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以借用一下卫生间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I use your restroom?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母肯定不会介意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the jellies wouldn't mind
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你做了一桌美味晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see you've made a delicious dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.74,0:15:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有没有兴趣来个特好吃的海霸球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I interest you in a mouthwatering chum ball
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,配着晚餐一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to go with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  好心的丑老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kind crone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不喜欢海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I don't like chum
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我这海霸球可是裹了糖衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But my chum balls are dipped in candy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸味的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chummy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃一小口应该没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess a little nibble wouldn't hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实在话  还挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That actually tastes pretty good
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.44,0:16:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你要永远脱水沉睡下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you'll be in a dehydrated sleep forever
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会是世上最方正的那一位了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:16.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'll be the squarest in the land
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘带镐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot my pickax
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个邪恶巫婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An evil witch?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贵重发箍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pricey hairband
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可拆卸鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,removable snoot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对帽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,party hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是邪恶巫婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not an evil witch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是邪恶皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're an evil queen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, you fool
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Queen?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow Yellow is in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow Yellow?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后害他脱水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Queen dried him out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.05,0:17:22.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且她好像还把水母堡全吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:22.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I think she ate all our jelly patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏皇后往那边走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad Queen went that-a-way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去逮住那个坏皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's hog-tie that royal pain in the caboose
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要甩掉那群笨水母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get away from those jelly brains
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一部童话见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See ya in the next fairy tale
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔镜魔镜挂墙上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic mirror on the wall--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最方正了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the squarest--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,jumpin' jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该按ESC键马上逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to hit my escape key
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,故事时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Story time's over
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干嘛把通道做成台阶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did I put in stairs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你无路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无路可逃的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来把你们这群水母压成酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to mush these jellies into marmalade
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螺丝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Screwdrivers?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别动我螺丝钉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not my screws
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,魔镜魔镜下墙来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Magic mirror off the wall
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个世上谁最快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's the fastest one of all?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要遭七年霉运了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seven years bad luck
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.37,0:19:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最方正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was the squarest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界待我不公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a world
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.17,0:19:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well then
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你翻不了页了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannot turn the page now, can you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皇后施下的沉睡魔咒仍未解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"While still under the Queen's sleeping spell
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,七只小水母把王子放上了海绵收纳盒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"the seven jellies placed the Prince in a sponge dish
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,避免王子发霉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep him from getting moldy"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄雪王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snow Yellow?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're still alive
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And naked
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure am
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几只小水母救了我一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little jellies saved my--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧穿上吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put these on, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  蟹蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:50.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Krusty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几只小水母救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You little jellies saved my sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're darn tootin'
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把那个坏皇后拆散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We took that rotten Queen apart--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一根螺丝一根螺丝地拆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:20:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bolt by bolt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她再也烦不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She won't bother you no more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就能来我的巢过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can all crash at my hive
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A-one, two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huzzah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们从此过上了幸福快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:09.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"And they all lived happily ever"--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.51,0:22:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My finger
